  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      MR saline peritoneography could be useful to demonstrate the peritoneal outline of the pouch
      of Douglas. The investigators think that the localization of the rectal tumor in function of
      this anatomic mark could be decisive for pre-operative assessment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
